By: Swami Sivananda
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
---
If the mind contents itself with sense objects, the concept of the reality of
the universe can only increase. If on the contrary, it thinks without cease
of Atma, the world will appear to it as a dream.
